# 🚀 Club Poster – Coding Ninjas 10X 🚀

An **interactive cyberpunk-themed poster** for the **Coding Ninjas 10X** event, built entirely with **HTML & CSS**.  
The poster features a **glitchy neon header, live countdown timer, and an RSVP QR code**, designed to resemble a futuristic terminal interface.

---

## 🌐 Live Demo

You can view the poster live using GitHub Pages:  
[https://prince-rai88.github.io/ClubPoster/poster3.html](https://prince-rai88.github.io/ClubPoster/poster3.html)

---

## ✨ Features

- **Cyberpunk terminal design** with neon glow effects.  
- **Glitch animation** for the main event title.  
- **Interactive RSVP QR code**.  
- **Live countdown timer** to the event.  
- Fully **responsive design** for desktop and mobile.  
- Smooth **hover animations** for buttons, cards, and QR code.  
- **Easy to customize**: colors, fonts, event details, and QR code.  
- Built entirely with **pure HTML & CSS**, no JavaScript frameworks required.

